rComments: I don't know if it was Fusco or the class but such a hard class to enjoy. Felt like a repeat of KPE100 with just a few more points that should have just been included in 100. rComments: One of the better profs in Kin. I took this course last year and she gave everyone a low mark on the book review because the class average was too high. I heard it was easier this year. Remember to read the papers because that's the only thing you will be tested on in the final.
